<!-- event-page: 申請端 - 上傳文件 -->

<main class="main">
	<div class="container">
        <div class="registration-hd">
			<hgroup>
                <h3 class="main-title">2020 年僑務委員會海外商會幹部暨青商培訓班</h3>
                <h5 class="sub-title">2020 Overseas Chamber of Commerce Cadre and Youth Business Training Program</h5>
			</hgroup>
            <div class="account dropdown">
                <a class="nav-link dropdown-toggle" href="#" id="navbarDropdownMenuLink" data-toggle="dropdown" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false" title="UserName">
                    <span>UserName</span>
                </a>
                <div class="dropdown-menu dropdown-menu-right" aria-labelledby="navbarDropdownMenuLink">
                    <a class="dropdown-item" href="#" title="登出">登出</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
		<div class="registration-wrapper">
			<div class="registration-inner">
                <div class="registration-nav">
                    <ul class="menu-item">
                        <li class="registration-item done">
                            <h5>
                                <small>1</small>
                                <span>申請表</span>
                            </h5>
                            <span class="brief">填寫各項基本資料及申請志願</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="registration-item current">
                            <h5>
                                <small>2</small>
                                <span>上傳文件</span>
                            </h5>
                            <span class="brief">上傳各項申請所需文件</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="registration-item">
                            <h5>
                                <small>3</small>
                                <span>確認資料</span>
                            </h5>
                            <span class="brief">確認步驟 1-3 各項資料及文件</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="registration-item">
                            <h5>
                                <small>4</small>
                                <span>送出申請</span>
                            </h5>
                            <span class="brief">確認步驟完成送出申請資料</span>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="registration-content">
                    <h4 class="warpper-title">上傳文件</h4>
					<p>請上傳下列各項文件，各別檔案請勿大於 5 MB。</p>
					<div class="lastchild-wrap">
                        <div class="application-block">
                            <h5 class="block-hd">資格審查文件</h5>
                            <div class="document-upload">
                                <div class="document-item">
                                    <div class="document-hd">
                                        <h5 class="document-title">護照影本</h5>
                                        <div class="document-action">
                                            <a href="#" class="btn btn-xs btn-info" title="檢視">檢視</a>
                                            <a href="#" class="btn btn-xs btn-secondary" title="修改">修改</a>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="document-bd">
                                        <p>僑民兒童於到校體驗前，須將護照影本及投保證明文件送媒合學校教務處註冊組，以利學校安排至校短期體驗相關事宜。另，體驗學生之班級安排以家長所填寫之申請表(表B)為主，惟學校仍可依學生實際學習情況進行調整。如未填列欲體驗之年級，校方即以體驗學生之年齡作為編班依據逕行安排。</p>
										<span class="upload-date">上傳時間: 2015/12/12 18:20</span>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                <div class="document-item">
                                    <div class="document-hd">
                                        <h5 class="document-title">投保證明文件</h5>
                                        <div class="document-action">
                                            <div class="file-wrap">
                                                <div class="md-form my-0">
                                                    <div class="file-field">
                                                        <div class="btn btn-primary btn-xs float-left waves-effect waves-light">
                                                            <span>選擇</span>
                                                            <input type="file" />
                                                        </div>
                                                        <div class="file-path-wrapper">
                                                            <input class="file-path validate" type="text" placeholder="選擇檔案" />
                                                        </div>
                                                    </div>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="document-bd">
                                        <p>請家長自行為學生投保在校體驗期間之意外險(含醫療險)，活動期間學員若宿疾復發或突發病症，送醫所需醫療等相關費用，應自行負擔。</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
					</div>
                </div>
			</div>
            <div class="form-action mt-0">
                <a href="#" class="btn btn-lg btn-primary" title="預覽各項資料">預覽各項資料</a>
            </div>
		</div>
    </div>
</main>



<% content_for :js do %>

<% end %>
